Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady, thanks for doing your duty for Britain this summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm a Alcott after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of the day, I simply want to be together \N with my special someone under the same sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Ichika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a week, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that he came out to greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't sit still, \Nknowing that you were returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't do that in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecilia? Cecilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm alright. I just felt a little dizzy for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, would you like to go to this tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Going out with you, Ichika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Cecilia Alcott, will be prepared for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this again. They aren't aware enough of their position as a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong, Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Laura, if you've got some time today,\N would you like to go clothes shopping with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My clothes are my military uniformâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But those are all uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You need more than military uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, summer break's almost over. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll leave around ten, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These clothes are for going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're still wearing a uniform, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, ever heard of Seaside Park's Dream CrÃªpes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat a mixed-berry one with the person you like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,your love will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! But it's always sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love will come true...Mixed-berry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, summer break is ending tomorrow,\Nand I still haven't made any memories with Ichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's why I chose to\N stay here instead of going back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed here instead of flying home, so I wish he'd initiate at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ichika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So which do you want Laura, skirt or pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Either iâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear Laura, you're just like Ichika when \N it comes to that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing for couples to be similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,First we'll get something for autumn-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I don't need autumn clothes just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can buy autumn wear in the autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, girls are supposed to \N get clothes a season ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's too late to get equipment\Nafter a war starts. Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's just look at everything then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect silver, and blonde too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I interest you in the newest clothing line?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's light and slightly transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,White is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad, but I'm already wearing white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here, why don't you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks, it'd be a hassâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a hassle at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may be wrong, but maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not attractive to boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I was going to get one, it might as well have been something cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Ichika would praise me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, that's a cute outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...the clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you're the cutest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going Laura? You finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have your uniform on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, maybe it didn't quite suit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...maybe something cuter would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! You want something cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...something that's a little revealing would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she's pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting the shoes out too huh? I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.64,UpTop,,0,0,0,,Should I take a photo of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.02,UpTop,,0,0,0,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.03,SIGN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,736)\c&H3E393B&\fax-0.25\blur1.5\fnLeviReBrushed\b1\fs80\3c&H9F9FAE&}NEVER FALTER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am both aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and unaware of the way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect the one who is close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think my breasts got bigger again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Houki? You in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Houki, I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...give me a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad. I didn't know you were in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda last minute, \Nso you don't have to if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've kept it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...it's like...\N I didn't want to get it dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be you just wanted Ichika to \Nbe the first person to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.67,SIGN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1314,410)\c&H000000&\blur0.8\fax-0.2\fs35\fnUn Dinaru\b1\frz348.1\3c&HDAD8CA&}Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to work part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I dressed as a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're much cooler and handsomer than those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would have preferred a maid uniform too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just this kind of person after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You look really good in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to CafÃ© @ Cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like black tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any requests, please let me know, Miladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want these hostages out alive, get us a car ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to leave off any tracking devices too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty. Bring me the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and drink it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw around, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Target 2, capture complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about on your end, Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Target 3, capture complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me! Being stopped by these brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All targets, capture complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Maid and Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, if find out we're Representative Cadets,\Nwe'll be in trouble, so we should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's leave it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather blow this place sky high and die
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,than get caught and spend the rest of my life in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wrists are next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two crÃªpes please, mixed-berry flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry, but we're already sold out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, you got anything in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, strawberry and blueberry please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is. This is my first time eating a crÃªpe, but I think it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll come here with Ichika next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hopefully they'll have mixed-berry in stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You had some sauce on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I know, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of my hands are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have a bite of my crÃªpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, about the crepe shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mixed-berry flavor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't even on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I didn't see any sauce\N  in the kitchen that would've been used for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so? You've got a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still got to have mixed berry, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Strawberries and blueberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know the secret of the mixed-berry\N flavor that's always sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating a mixed-berry crÃªpe with your\N boyfriend would be nice, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What...is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure these are pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, you look so good in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold me like that! It's hard to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cats are supposed sit nice and quietly on people's laps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,Note: In Japanese, "nyan" is the sound of a cat's meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say "nyan" to get into character?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to do stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But it'd be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, c'mon, say it. "Nyan."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ny-nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, you're too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are some unusual outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A black cat and a white cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you look, how do I put it, interesting....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and rather cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really? So we're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...then it's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wear it every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. It's tomorrow but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruder detected in Area 6-D!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercept immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat: Intruder detected in Area 6-D!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercept immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Your body has been fitted \Nwith supervisory nanomachines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry out your mission as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't kill me, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl, M.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking on an IS suit-less?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to take the IS\N that's been sealed away in this base...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Infinite Stratos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent Zephyrus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Phantom Task?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichika was surprisingly aggressive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so helpless, getting flustered asking me on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Dan and the others as well while I was at it, but they said they couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the idiot for expecting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Playing with the hearts of girls, you're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You fail as a bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Now, shall we hurry and head to the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:22.00,UpTop,,0,0,0,,Quickly! Quickly! Quickly! Quickly! Quickly! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you're in a hurry to go in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.64,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecilia's a nice person for buying us these, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.02,0:24:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.78,0:24:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to split into two groups and look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pools really are the best in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.84,0:25:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I haven't seen anyone up until now. Are you sure they're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.76,0:25:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.20,0:25:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's odd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.42,0:25:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.02,0:25:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. They're not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.02,0:25:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.56,0:25:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That really was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.34,0:25:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Orimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.10,0:25:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nohohon-san! You all came!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.90,0:25:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the girls from the IS Academy are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, captain, Cecelia's wearing a perverted swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:25:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:25:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How erotic, Cecilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.18,0:26:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.88,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Orimu, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.96,0:26:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.06,0:26:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.98,0:26:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.86,0:26:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called the pair-slide course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.82,0:26:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.08,0:26:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice. I guess we can slide together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.32,0:26:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair, Houki!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.06,0:26:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play Rock-Paper-Scissors for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:26:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.98,0:27:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock-Paper-Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.88,0:27:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me explain the pair-slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.96,0:27:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the guy sits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.94,0:27:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.72,0:27:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the girl sits between his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.34,0:27:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.26,0:27:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.78,0:27:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the guy holds the girl tightly from behind, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.64,0:27:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Embrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.32,0:27:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.42,0:27:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.70,0:27:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.42,0:27:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.78,0:27:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's dangerous so you need to stay close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.94,0:27:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, enjoy the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Ichika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.38,0:28:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not on purp-
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.78,0:28:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika, you perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.80,0:28:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.78,0:28:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was inevitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still touched them...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.80,0:28:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Ichika. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let me explain the pair-slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.06,0:28:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the guy sits down. Then, the girl sits between his legs and the guy grabs her from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.96,0:28:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Houki?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.40,0:28:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind sitting behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.52,0:28:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.90,0:29:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well the water's pretty strong;
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.58,0:29:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be best for you to hide your face behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.02,0:29:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I got ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The tighter you hold on, the safer you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.31,0:29:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.50,0:29:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.76,0:29:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.48,0:29:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, enjoy the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was really fast, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.24,0:29:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.10,0:29:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No...umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your back's...gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.42,0:29:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.16,0:29:57.52,UpTop,,0,0,0,,Ichika! Hurry and get up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.82,0:29:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.16,0:30:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, running into them even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.82,0:30:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Orimura-sensei, is it okay that you aren't with Ichika-kun? He is your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.08,0:30:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my day off. If I have to deal with them it'll be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.36,0:30:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll head there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.92,0:30:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Is it an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.96,0:30:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.48,0:30:47.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,Green Day Market
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.04,0:31:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty! What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.24,0:31:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.54,0:31:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called goldfish-scooping.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.70,0:31:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You use this to scoop goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika, teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.62,0:31:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.46,0:31:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Wait your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.86,0:31:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.66,0:31:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If this happens, it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.98,0:31:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.70,0:31:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the devil fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.06,0:31:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat the octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is traditional Japanese food.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.12,0:31:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty, isn't it? See, Laura?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.42,0:31:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.24,0:31:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn to say "ahhn" at Houki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.02,0:31:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika-san, "ahhn".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.02,0:32:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can shoot sharper than I!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a toy gun, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.72,0:32:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, as expected of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.08,0:32:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also pretty good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some marksmanship training in the military, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Houki.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.64,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
